{"tid":2230810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"床位呎租106元 劏房貴過豪宅  基層花四成人工交租 越住越細","createTime":"2020-10-05T07:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:42:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"392cac578e93959d5c90e6199c7a6e0476763bbe","tid":2230810,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/TT2FGG3WZFHXXPPVRKJC3SCC7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FTT2FGG3WZFHXXPPVRKJC3SCC7A%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=8105ff9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FTT2FGG3WZFHXXPPVRKJC3SCC7A%2F&h=b3c3bc15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/TT2FGG3WZFHXXPPVRKJC3SCC7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n床位呎租106元 劏房貴過豪宅 <br />\n基層花四成人工交租 越住越細<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫情下不少基層家庭收入大減，惟租金卻不減反升。社區組織協會調查發現，基層開工不足，不適切居所住戶租金佔入息比例中位數由過去29%急升至39%，單身及二人家庭的有關比率更高達45%及50%；而不適切居所呎租繼續高於私樓，其中面積僅18呎的床位呎租升至105.6元，60呎的板房或梗房呎租亦達50.7元，遠高於千呎豪宅35.5元的呎租。社協擔心基層無力交租下，只能搬到更細的不適切居所，形成惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：無良業主加租67% 濫收「走廊費」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AWkUZ7FUTMRvCSsZ41I4mTndTyE=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YX5IYCYY2ZGN5BABK2ZTJVRZ3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAWkUZ7FUTMRvCSsZ41I4mTndTyE%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYX5IYCYY2ZGN5BABK2ZTJVRZ3Q.jpg&h=52c8a0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本港住屋「越細越貴」問題惡化，床位呎租高過豪宅。<br />\n<br />\n社協上月向不適切居所住戶進行網上問卷調查，收回439份問卷。綜合差餉物業估價處今年8月數字，發現本港住屋「越細越貴」問題惡化。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於60呎板房或梗房8月時的平均呎租為50.7元，是第二貴租的單位類型，租金較去年9月升2.8%。面積135呎劏房呎租為37.5元，與430呎以下的九龍區私樓呎租相同。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：團體倡Ｎ無津貼恒常化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3cjqEDEb0R-B0DeVNH9Cj_b5j1M=/1781x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3STWJM6TINGCTKPCII5MCRVRQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3cjqEDEb0R-B0DeVNH9Cj_b5j1M%3D%2F1781x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3STWJM6TINGCTKPCII5MCRVRQQ.jpg&h=d6e5d3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■呂綺珊（前排右三）指不少劏房業主大幅加租，增基層負擔。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，46.5%受訪者過去三年曾被業主加租，當中10%人三年內被加租三次，亦有受訪者三年內累積加租達1,500元，或一次性加租1,100元。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n社協幹事呂綺珊表示，受疫情影響，不少基層開工不足甚至失業，收入大減，最新基層住戶租金佔入息比例中位數升至39%，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z6XtzrToRTbDax-XCRYp6SX2kds=/960x1769/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IFL4AFQRBNH5ZLZC7WSJGQEO2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz6XtzrToRTbDax-XCRYp6SX2kds%3D%2F960x1769%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIFL4AFQRBNH5ZLZC7WSJGQEO2Q.jpg&h=8c6cb991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團體促設租務管制<br />\n<br />\n呂綺珊說，香港居住面積越細呎租越貴的問題不斷惡化，因為本港缺乏租金管制，加上公屋供應嚴重不足，劏房需求殷切，不少劏房業主「獅子開大口」，大幅加租，並濫收水電費和其他雜費等，基層只能「肉隨砧板上」。<br />\n<br />\n關注基層住屋聯席提議設立租務管制，成立由租客與業主比例為一比一的法定委員會，。。。。。。。。。"}]}